data.description: Welcome to this Warming and beautiful, energy-efficient home in the desirable community of Desert Sky Ranch! This Stunning single story 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath with Ivory walls, 2 Car Garage with North/South exposure. Boasting an open concept layout with vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting and a Fan in every room.Charming kitchen with upgraded cabinets and Fully formed Granite & Engineered stone. A large island with casual seating, pantry, separate dining area and Whirlpool appliances. Spacious split bedrooms. Owner suite features a spacious full bath with Garden tub, step-in shower, private toilet room, and walk in closet. Covered patio is sized right for your morning coffee or dining alfresco. Ask about special Rebates to help with lowering interest rates. Hydro quad water processor for the whole home and ADT security.  GE washer and Dryer included. Low maintenance desert landscaping in front, seeded lawn and rock in back. Community features walking paths, a large park and playground. Located close to Lucid, Abbott and an easy commute to Chandler. Close proximity to Dave White Regional Park, golf course and much more..
